data.chText: 热带的；来自热带的；产于热带的
data.enText: coming from, found in or typical of the tropics

simple_means.memory_skill: tropic 回归线 + al …的→ 回归线附近的 → 热带的

tr: hot and humid as in the tropics
characterized by or of the nature of a trope or tropes
relating to or situated in or characteristic of the tropics (the region on either side of the equator)
of or relating to the tropics, or either tropic

value.def: Tropical means belonging to or typical of the tropics.

example.ex: ...a plan to preserve the world's tropical forests.
example.tran: 保护世界热带雨林的计划

value.def: Tropical weather is hot and damp weather that people believe to be typical of the tropics.
value.tran: 湿热的;典型热带气候的

partsOfSpeech.dec: trop 转 + e → 转出来的意义 → 转义
troph 营养 + y 表名词 → 经过轮番努力而得到的东西 → 奖品
trop 转 + ic 某种药 → 回归线
tropic 回归线 + al …的，具有…性质的 → 回归线附近的 → 热带的
